hadiths[132]{hadithnumber,text}:
495,"Imam ibne Shahaab Zohri sey riwayat hai ke hazart umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi Alaih) (Madina ke governer) ney Asr ki namaz waqt sey kuchh muakhkhar (deri) ki to Hazrat Urwa ney un sey farmaya : Jibril alehissalam utrey they aur unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key aagey khadey ho kar aap ko namaz padhaai thi. umr bin Abdul-Azeez kehney lagey : Urwa dekho ! kya keh rahey ho? unhoney kaha : mainey Bashir bin Abu-Masood ko ye kehtey huye suna ke mainey Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huye suna ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna : Jibril alehissalam utrey aur mujhey namaz padhaai. mainey unkey sath namaz padhi, phir mainey unkey sath namaz padhi, phir mainey unkey sath namaz padhi, phir mainey unkey sath namaz padhi, phir mainey unkey sath namaz padhi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni ungliyon par paanchon namazein shumar kin."
496,"Sayyar bin Sulama sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey apney walid mohtaram ko Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key barey mein sawal kartey suna. (Sayyar key shagrid Shoba kehtey hain ke) mainey (Sayyar sey) kaha : kya aap ney un (apney baap) sey suna hai? unhon (Sayyar) ney kaha : (mainey isi tarah suna hai) jis tarah main is waqt tum sey sun raha hun. kaha : mainey apney walid sey suna, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key barey mein sawal kar rahey they to Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki namaz ko nisf (aadhi) raat tak muakhkhar (der) karney mein koi parwa nahin kartey they. aap Isha ki namaz sey pehley soney aur namaz key baad baaten karna pasand nahin farmatey they. Shoba kehtey hain : ba'd Azan main un (Sayyar) sey mila to mainey (bator wasooq (yaqeen) Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees key barey mein) phir sawal kiya to unhon (Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu)) ney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki namaz us waqt padhtey jab suraj dhal jata aur Asr ki namaz us waqt padhtey ke (aap key sath namaz padhney wala) aadmi Madina Munawra ki door daraz basti tak pahunch jata tha jab ke abhi suraj tez hota tha. aur Maghrib key barey mein mujhey ilm nahin ke unhoney kon sa waqt zikr kiya. phir main uskey baad unhein mila to un sey puchha farmaney lagey : aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah ki namaz us waqt padhtey ke namazi salam pher kar apney hum nasheen jisey wo pehley sey pahchaantaa tha, key chehrey ko dekhta to usey pehchan leta tha aur aap subah ki namaz mein saath (60) sey sau (100) tak aayaat tilawat farmatey they."
497,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) suraj dhalney key waqt (apney hujrey mubaraka sey) nikley aur unhein namaz Zohar padhaai.
498,"Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zamin key garm honey ka shikwa kya lekin aap ney hamari shikayat door na ki. abu-Is-haq sey kaha gaya : (sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ka shikwa ) namaz jaldi padhney key barey mein tha? unhoney kaha : haan."
499,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi manzil mein utartey they to Zohar ki namaz padhney sey pehley wahan sey kooch na farmatey they. eik aadmi ney kaha : agar-che suraj sar par hota? farmaya : agar-che suraj sar par hota.
500,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab garmi hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz Zohar ko thandi kar key padhtey they aur jab sardi hoti to jaldi padhtey
501,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab garmi ziyada ho to namaz ko thandi karo kyonkey garmi ki shiddat jahannam ka josh hai."
502,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooa riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Zohar ki namaz ( kuch ) thandak mein padho kyonkey jo garmi tum mehsus kartey ho, wo jahannam ka josh hai."
503,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye Jibril alehissalam hain jo tumhein tumhara Deen sikhaney aaye hain, phir junhi Fajr tulu hui unhoney subh ki namaz aur jab suraj dhal gaya to Zohar ki namaz padhaai, phir Asr ki namaz padhaai jab unhoney har chiz ka saya uskey barabar (zawal key saye key ilawa ) dekh liya, phir maghrib ki namaz padhaai junhi suraj ghurub huwa aur rozey daar key liye roza kholna halal ho gaya, phir Isha ki namaz padhaai jab raat ki surkhii ghaaieb ho gaee. phir agley din wo (Jibreel alehissalam ) dobara aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur aap ko subh ki namaz padhaai jab thodi si roshni phel gaee thi, phir aap ko Zohar ki namaz padhaai jab har chiz ka saya uskey barabar ho gaya, phir Asr ki namaz padhaai jab har chiz ka saya dugna ho gaya, phir maghrib ki namaz kal waley waqt hi par padhaai, yani jab suraj ghurub ho gaya aur rozey daar key liye roza kholna halal ho gaya, phir Isha ki namaz padhaai jab raat ka kuch hissa guzar gaya, phir farmaya : har namaz ka waqt tumhari kal aur aaj ki namaz ka darmiyani waqt hai."
504,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki Zohar ki namaz garmiyon mein teen sey paanch qadam key b-qadr ( saye mein) aur sardiyon mein paanch sey saat qadam key b-qadr ( saye mein) hoti thi."
505,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey namazon key oqaat key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : merey sath namaz padho. aap ney Zohar ki namaz padhaai jab suraj dhal gaya aur Asr ki namaz padhaai jab har chiz ka saya uskey barabar ho gaya aur maghrib ki namaz padhaai jab suraj ghurub ho gaya. aur Isha ki namaz padhaai jab shafaq ghurub ho gaee. aur ( agley din ) aap ney namaz Zohar padhaai jab insan ka saya uskey barabar ho gaya aur Asr ki namaz padhaai jab insan ka saya us sey dugna ho gaya aur maghrib ki namaz ghurub shafaq sey thodi der pehley padhaai aur Isha ki namaz tihai raat key waqt padhaai.
506,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr ki namaz padhi jab ke dhoop abhi hujrey Aaisha mein thi, yani saya unkey hujrey sey bahar nahin nikla tha."
507,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Asr ki namaz ada farmatey phir janey wala Quba tak jata. (Zohri aur Is-haq mein sey) eik ney kaha : wo unkey paas pahunchta to abhi wo namaz Asr padh rahey hotey they. aur dusrey ney kaha : aur suraj abhi ooncha hota tha.
508,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Asr ki namaz ada farmatey they jab ke suraj kafi buland aur tez hota tha. aap key sath namaz padhney wala awaali ko jata to suraj abhi ooncha hota tha.
509,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamein Asr ki namaz padhaatey to suraj safed aur buland hota tha.
510,"Abu-Umaama bin Sahal bayan kartey hain ke hamney Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi Alaih) key sath Zohar ki namaz padhi, phir hum nikley yahan tak ke Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas pahunchey to hamney unhein Asr ki namaz padhtey paya. mainey kaha : chacha jaan ! ye kon si namaz aap ney padhi hai? unhoney farmaya : Asr ki. aur ye Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz hai jo hum (aap key sath ) padhtey they."
511,Hazrat Abu-Salma sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke hamney Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi Alaih) key daur (govornari) mein namaz padhi phir hum Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf chaley hamney unhein namaz padhtey paya. jab wo farigh huye to hamein kehney lagey : tum ney namaz padh li hai? hamney kaha : hamney Zohar ki namaz padhi hai. wo kehney lagey : mainey to Asr ki namaz padhi hai. logon ney kaha : aap ney jaldi ki hai. unhoney farmaya : main to is tarah namaz padhta hun jis tarah mainey apney sathiyon ko padhtey dekha hai.
512,"Hazrat Ala bin Abdur-Rehman ney kaha ke wo Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas Basra mein unkey ghar gaey jab ke wo ( Ala ) Zohar sey farigh huye they, aur Hazrat Anas ka ghar masjid key sath hi tha. jab hum aap key paas gaey to aap ney farmaya : kya tum ney Asr ki namaz padh li hai? hamney kaha : nahin, hum to Zohar ki namaz padh kar aaye hain. aap ney farmaya : phir Asr ki namaz padho. hum uthey aur Asr ki namaz padhi. jab hum farigh huye to aap ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna : ye munafiq ki namaz hai. wo betha Asr ki namaz ka intizar karta rehta hai yahan tak ke jab suraj shetan key do seengon key darmiyan ho jata hai to wo uthta hai, chaar thogein maarta hai aur us doran mein Allah ka zikr bhi nahin karta magar thoda."
513,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis sey Asr ki namaz reh jaey, wo yun samjhey ke uskey ehal o ayaal aur ghar baar lut gaey."
514,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Jibril alehissalam Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aap ko namaz key oqaat batlaey key liye aaye. Jibril aagey khadey huye, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey peechey aur log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey they. is tarah aap ney Zohar ki namaz us waqt padhi jab suraj dhala, phir jab har shakhs ka saya uskey barabar ho gaya ( saya zawal key ilawa ) to Jibril phir aaye aur isi tarah kya jis tarah ( Zohar key waqt) kya tha, yani Jibril aagey ho gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey peechey aur log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey. is tarah Asr ki namaz padhi. phir jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to Jibril aaye, aagey khadey huye, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey peechey aur log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey they, chunanche (is tarah) maghrib ki namaz padhi. phir jab suraj ki surkhi ghaayeb ho gaee to Jibril aaye, aagey khadey huye, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey peechey aur log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey they. is tarah Isha ki namaz padhi. phir jab Fajr ki roshni phooti to Jibril aaye, aagey khadey ho gaey. unkey peechey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey log khadey ho gaey aur Fajr ki namaz ada ki. phir doosrey din Jibril us waqt aaye jab har aadmi ka saya uskey qad key barabar ho gaya aur isi tarah kya jis tarah kal kya tha aur Zohar ki namaz padhi. phir aaye jab har aadmi ka saya uskey qad sey dugna ho gaya aur isi tarah kya jis tarah kal kya tha aur Asr ki namaz padhi. phir aaye jab suraj ghurub ho gaya aur isi tarah kya jis tarah kal kya tha aur maghrib ki namaz padhi, phir hum so gaey, phir uthey (magar wo abhi na aaye they) hum phir so gaey, phir uthey to Jibril aaye aur isi tarah kya jis tarah kal kya tha aur Isha ki namaz padhi. phir aaye jab Fajr phel gaee thi aur roshni ho gaee thi aur sitarey ghaney nazar aa rahey they aur isi tarah kya jaisey kal kya tha aur subh ki namaz padhi. phir farmaya : (aaj aur kal ki) do namazon ka darmiyani waqt har namaz ka waqt hai."
515,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Asr ki do rakatein suraj ghurub honey sey pehley padh lein ya subh ki eik rakat suraj tulu honey sey pehley padh li to usney namaz paa li."
516,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs suraj ghurub honey sey qabl Asr ki namaz sey eik rakat paa ley ya suraj tulu honey sey qabl subh ki eik rakat paa ley to yaqinan us ney wo namaz paa li."
517,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs Asr ki namaz ki pehli rakat suraj ghurub honey sey pehley paa ley to wo baqi namaz puri karey aur jab subh ki namaz ki pehli rakat suraj tulu honey sey pehley paa ley to wo baqi namaz puri kerey. (uski namaz faasid na hogi)."
518,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney subh ki namaz ki eik rakat tulu shams sey qabl paa li to usney sari namaaze-subh paa li aur jisney Asr ki namaz ki eik rakat ghuroobe-shams sey pehley paa li to usney puri namaaz Asr paa li.
519,Hazrat Muaz sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Muaz bin ifraa (Raziallahu anhu) key sath tawaf kya aur ( do rakat ) namaz na padhi. mainey kaha : aap ( tawaf ki do rakat ) namaz nahin padhengey ? wo farmaney lagey : tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : Asr key baad ( nafl ) namaz na padhi jaey yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey aur subh key baad bhi ( nafl ) namaz na padhi jaey yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho jaey.
520,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap sey namazon key oqaat (waqt) key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : hamarey paas aainda do din thehro. aap ney (pehley din) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney Fajr hotey hi iqaamat kahi aur aap ney Fajr ki namaz padhaai. phir junhi suraj dhalaa to aap ney unhein iqaamat ka hukm diya aur Zohar ki namaz padaahi. phir jab suraj ko safed dekha (tapish dophare sey kam hui) to iqaamat ka hukm diya aur Asr ki namaz padhi. phir jab suraj ka aakhiri kinara doob gaya to iqaamat ka hukm diya aur maghrib ki namaz padhaai. phir jab suraj ki surkhi ghaaieb ho gaee to Isha ki iqaamat kahlwaai. phir agley din usey (takheer ka) hukm diya aur Fajr ko roshni mein padha. phir Zohar ko thanda kiya aur khub achchhi tarah thanda kiya. phir Asr ki namaz padhi jab ke suraj abhi safed tha (zard na huwa tha). wesey pehley din sey muakhkhar (der) kiya. phir shafaq (surkhi) ghaaieb honey sey pehley maghrib ki namaz padhi. phir aap ney un (Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu)) ko hukm diya to unhoney Isha ki iqaamat kahi jab ke tihai raat guzar chuki thi aur aap ney Isha ki namaz padhi. phir farmaya : kahan hai wo shakhs jisney namazon key oqaat key barey mein puchha tha? (usey laya gaya to aap ney farmaya :) tumhaari namazon key oqaat (waqt) in (do dino ki namazon) key darmiyan mein hain jo tum ney dekhey.
521,Banu Aslam key eik shakhs sey riwayat hai jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba mein sey they ( farmatey hain ke ) Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Maghrib ki namaz padh kar Madina Munawra key door daraz ilaqon mein apney ghar walon ki taraf wapis laut'tey (to itni roshni hoti thi ke) wo teer chalatey to teer girney ki jagah dekh saktey they.
522,Hazrat Abu-Basra Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum ko (makhmas) maqam mein Asr ki namaz padhaai phir farmaya : tehqiq ye namaz tum sey pehley logon (Bani-Israel) par muqarrar ki gaee thi magar wo isey zaya kar bethey (waqt par ada na ki). jo aadmi isey pabandi sey bar-waqt ada kerega usey dohra ajr milega aur uskey baad (nafl) namaz jayez nahin yahan tak ke shaahid tulu ho. shaahid sey murad sitaara hai.
523,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu Anhuma sey riwayat hai. (Hadees key raawi) Shoba kehtey hain ke Qatada mazkura riwayat ko kabhi marfooa bayan kartey hain aur kabhi marfooa bayan nahin kartey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Zohar ki namaz ka waqt baqi rehta hai jab tak Asr ka waqt shuru na ho aur Asr ki namaz ka waqt baqi rehta hai jab tak suraj zard na ho aur Maghrib ki namaz ka waqt baqi rehta hai jab tak surkhi ki ziyadti khatam na ho aur Isha ka waqt baqi rehta hai jab tak raat nisf (aadhi) na ho aur subah ka waqt baqi rehta hai jab tak suraj tulu na ho.
524,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik shakhs aaya jo aap sey namazon key oqaat (waqt) key barey mein sawal kar raha tha. aap ney usey kuchh jawab na diya (balke) junhi Fajr (po) phati aap ney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya aur unhoney subah ki iqaamat kahi. phir jab suraj dhalaa to aap ney unhein hukm diya to unhoney Zohar ki iqaamat kahi aur kehney wala kehta tha ke din nisf (aadha) ho gaya hai jab ke aap khub jantey they. phir aap ney unhein hukm diya to unhoney Asr ki iqaamat kahi jab ke suraj kafi buland tha. phir aap ney unhein hukm diya to unhoney Maghrib ki iqaamat kahi junhi suraj ghurub huwa. phir aap ney unhein hukm diya to unhoney Isha ki iqaamat kahi jab surkhi ghaaieb hui. phir aap ney unhein agley din Fajr (ki iqaamat) ka hukm diya. jab (namaz sey) farigh huye to kehney wala kehta tha ke suraj tulu ho gaya. phir Zohar ki namaz ko guzishta kal ki Asr key waqt key qarib tak muakhkhar (deri) kiya. phir Asr ko muakhkhar kiya yahan tak ke jab farigh huye to kehney wala kehta tha : suraj surkh ho gaya. phir Maghrib ko muakhkhar (deri) kiya yahan tak ke surkhi ghaaieb honey ko thi. phir Isha ko tihai raat tak muakhkhar (deri) kiya. phir farmaya : namazon key oqaat (waqt) in do dino ki namazon key darmiyan hain.
525,"Basheer bin Salam ney kaha ke main aur Hazrat Muhammad bin Ali (Baaqar) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Ansari Raziallahu Anhuma key paas gaey aur un sey kaha : hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key barey mein bataaiye aur ye Hujjaaj bin Yusuf ka daur tha. unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur Zohar ki namaz padhi jab suraj dhal gaya aur abhi saya tasmey key barabar tha. phir Asr ki namaz padhi jabkey saya aadmi key qad aur eik tasmey key barabar tha (eik misl sey eik tasmey ki miqdaar key barabar bada tha). phir Maghrib ki namaz padhi jab suraj ghurub ho gaya. phir Isha ki namaz padhi jab surkhi ghaaieb hui. phir Fajr ki namaz padhi jab Fajr tulu hui. phir agley din Zohar ki namaz padhi jab saya aadmi key qad key barabar tha. phir Asr ki namaz padhi jab aadmi ka saaya dugna ho gaya aur itna waqt baqi tha ke eik oont sawar darmiyani tez chaal sey Zul-Hulefa pahunch sakta tha, phir Maghrib ki namaz padhi jab suraj doob chuka tha, phir Isha ki namaz tihai ya nisf (aadhi) raat key waqt padhi, phir Fajr ki namaz khub roshni mein padhi."
526,"Hazrat Sayyar bin Sulama bayan kartey hain ke main (apney walid key sath) Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya. merey walid mohtaram ney un sey puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farz namazein kaisey padha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap Zohar ki namaz jisey tum oola (paisheen) kehtey ho, us waqt padhtey they jab suraj dhalta tha aur Asr ki namaz us waqt padhtey they ke (namaz key baad) hum mein sey koi shakhs Madiney ki intehai door wali aas-paas ki basti mein apney ghar wapis pahunch jata tha jabkey suraj abhi zinda hota tha, aur main bhool gaya ke Maghrib key barey mein unhoney kya farmaya. aur aap achchha samajhtey they ke Isha ki namaz ko jisey tum utma (andheri) kehtey ho, der sey padhein aur aap Isha ki namaz sey pehley soney aur baad mein baaten karney ko napasand kartey they. aur aap subah ki namaz sey farigh hotey they to aadmi apney hum nasheen ko pehchan sakta tha. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) saath sey sau aayaat tak (namaze Fajr mein) tilawat farmaya kartey they."
527,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Jibril alehissalam zawal shams key waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! uthiye aur Zohar ki namaz padhiye jab suraj dhal gaya. phir thehrey yahan tak ke jab aadmi ka saya uskey barabar ho gaya to wo Asr ki namaz key liye aap key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! uthiye aur Asr ki namaz padhiye. phir kuchh der thehrey yahan tak ke jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to phir aaye aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! uthiye aur Maghrib ki namaz padhiye. aap uthey aur Maghrib ki namaz padhi jab suraj pura doob gaya. phir thehrey yahan tak ke jab surkhi ghaaieb ho gaee to phir aap key paas aaye aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! uthiye aur Isha ki namaz padhiye. aap uthey aur aap ney Isha ki namaz padhi. phir aap key paas aaye jab subah ko Fajr ki roshni chamak uthi aur kaha : uthiye aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur namaz padhiye. aap uthey aur subah ki namaz padhi. phir agley din aap key paas aaye jab har aadmi ka saya uskey barabar ho gaya aur kaha : uthiye aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! aur namaz padhiye to aap ney Zohar ki namaz padhi. phir aap key paas Jibril alehissalam aaye jab aadmi ka saya dugna ho gaya aur kaha : uthiye aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! aur namaz padhiye. to aap ney Asr ki namaz padhi, phir wo maghrib ki namaz key liye aap key paas aaye jab suraj ghurub huwa kal waley waqt par hi aur kaha : uthiye aur namaz padhiye to aap ney maghrib ki namaz padhi. phir wo Isha ki namaz key liye aap key paas aaye jab raat ka pehla tihai hissa guzar chuka tha aur kaha : uthiye aur namaz padhiye to aap ney Isha ki namaz padhi. phir wo subah ki namaz key liye aap key paas aaye jab khub roshni ho chuki thi aur kaha : uthiye aur namaz padhiye to aap ney subah ki namaz padhi. phir Jibril kehney lagey : tamam namazon ka waqt in do dino ki namazon key darmiyan mein hai."
528,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki namaz dophare key waqt padhtey they aur Asr ki namaz padhtey to suraj (zardi sey) saaf aur safed hota tha aur Maghrib ki namaz padhtey jab suraj doob jata aur Isha ki namaz (mukhtalif oqaat (waqt) mein padhtey) jab dekhtey ke sab jama ho gaey hain to jaldi padh letey aur jab dekhtey ke unhoney takheer ki hai to der sey padhtey.
529,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : main sab logon sey ziyada us namaz yani Isha key waqt ko janta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye namaz teesri raat ka chaand ghurub honey par padhtey they."
530,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah ki qism ! bilashuba main us namaz yani Ishaey-aakhira key waqt ko sab logon sey ziyada janta hun. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye namaz teesri raat ka chaand ghurub honey par padhtey they.
531,"Hazrat Sayyar bin Sulama sey riwayat hai ke main aur merey walid mohtaram Hazrat Abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey. merey walid mohtaram ney un sey kaha : bataiye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farz namazein kaisey padhtey they? unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) dophare ki namaz (Zohar)  jisey tum oola (pesheen) kehtey ho, us waqt padhtey jab suraj dhal jata aur Asr ki namaz us waqt padhtey ke hum mein sey koi shakhs (aap key sath namaz padhney key baad) Madiney ki intehai door wali aas-paas ki basti mein apney ghar ko jata tha to us waqt bhi suraj zinda hota tha aur main bhool gaya ke maghrib key barey mein aap ney kya farmaya? aur aap Isha ki namaz jisey tum utma kehtey ho, der sey padhna achchha samajhtey they aur Isha ki namaz sey pehley sona aur baad mein baaten karna napasand farmatey they aur subah ki namaz sey farigh hotey to aadmi apney hum nasheen (sathi) ko pehchan sakta tha aur aap saath sey sau aayaat tak namaz mein tilawat farmatey they."
532,"Janab ibne Juraij bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Ata sey puchha : kon sa waqt aap ziyada munasib samajhtey hain ke main is mein Isha ki namaz padhun chahey Imam hun ya akela? unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ko ye farmatey huye suna ke eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Isha ko muakhkhar (deri) kiya yahan tak ke log sau gaey, phir jaagey (magar aap abhi tak tashrif na laye they, lihaza) phir sau gaey, phir jaagey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney khadey ho kar pukara : (aey Allah key Rasool !) namaz ! namaz ! (namaz key liye tashrif laaiye !) Ata ney kaha : Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya ke phir Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye. mujhey yun mehsus hota hai ke main ab bhi aap ko dekh raha hun ke aap key sar mubarak sey pani key qatrey gir rahey they aur aap ney apna haath sar ki eik janib rakha huwa tha, phir aap ney ishara kiya. (ibn Juraij ney kaha : ) mainey Ata sey puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apna daste-mubarak kis tarah sar par rakha huwa tha? Ata ney merey samney is tarah ishara kiya jis tarah ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kiya tha. Ata ney apni ungliyan kuch kholein phir unhein sar par rakha ke aap ki ungliyon key kinarey sar key agley hissey tak pahunchtey they, phir us (Ataa) ney apni ungliyan mila lein aur unhein is tarah sar par sey guzaaraa ke aap key angoothey kaan key us kinarey ko lagey jo chehrey ki janib hai, phir kanpati aur maathe key kinarey ko lagey. wo zarra bhar bhi kami beshi na kartey they balke bilkul isi tarah phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye khatra na hota ke main apni ummat ko mashaqqat mein dal dunga to main unhein hukm deta ke wo zarur isi waqt namaz padha karen."
533,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik raat Isha ki namaz muakhkhar ki yahan tak ke raat ka kafi hissa guzar gaya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huye aur buland aawaz sey pukara, aey Allah key Rasool ! namaz key liye tashrif laaiye. aurten aur bachey so gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to pani key qatrey aap key sar sey gir rahey they aur aap farma rahey they : ye hai Isha ki namaz ka asal waqt agar mujhey apni ummat par mashaqqat ka khatra na hota."
534,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki namaz ko der sey padha kartey they."
535,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye khatra na hota ke main apni ummat ko mashaqqat mein dal dunga to main unhein Isha ki namaz muakhkhar karney aur har namaz key waqt miswak karney ka hukm deta."
536,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik raat Isha ki namaz muakhkhar ki to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pukara ke aurten aur bachey so gaey. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : tumharey ilawa koi us namaz ka intizar nahin kar raha. aur un dino Madina Munawra key ilawa kahin namaz na padhi jati thi. phir aap ney farmaya is namaz ko surkhi ghaaieb honey sey ley kar tihai raat tak padho. ye alfaz ibne-Hamir key hain.
537,"ummul-Mominin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik raat Isha ki namaz ko muakhkhar farmaya yahan tak ke bahut raat guzar gaee aur masjid waley ( khususan aurten aur bachey ) so gaey, phir aap tashrif laye aur namaz padhaai aur farmaya : bilashuba yehi hai us ka ( asal ) waqt agar mujhey apni ummat par mashaqqat ka khatra na hota."
538,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik raat bahut der tak Isha ki namaz key liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka intizar kartey rahey. jab tihai ya us sey kuch ziyada raat guzar gaee to aap tashrif laye aur aatey hi farmaya : tum aisi namaz ka intizar kar rahey ho jiska intizar tumharey ilawa kisi aur Deen waley nahin kar rahey hain aur agar meri ummat par us waqt namaz padhna bojhal na hota to main yaqinan unhein us waqt namaz parhata. phir aap ney muazzan ko hukm diya to usney iqaamat kahi, phir aap ney namaz padhaai."
539,"Hazrat abu-Saeed khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen maghrib ki namaz padhaai, phir hamari taraf nahin nikley yahan tak ke raat ka kafi hissa guzar gaya, phir aap tashrif laye aur unhein (sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko) namaz padhaai, phir farmaya : log to namaz padh kar so gaey magar tum namaz hi mein rahey jab tak namaz ka intizar kartey rahey aur agar kamzor ki kamzori aur bimar ki bimari madde-nazar na hoti to main us namaz ko nisf raat tak muakhkhar karney ka hukm deta."
540,"Hazrat Humed bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney anguthi banwai ? unhoney farmaya : han, aap ney eik raat Isha ki namaz taqriban nisf raat tak muakhkhar ki. jab namaz padh chukey to aap ney apna chehra hamari taraf kya aur farmaya : tum jab tak namaz ka intizar kartey rahey, namaz hi mein rahey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey yun mehsus hota hai ke main ab bhi aap ki anguthi ki chamak dekh raha hun. Ali, yani ibne-Hajar ki hadees key alfaz hain : nisf raat tak."
541,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar log Azan kehney aur saf awwal mein khadey honey ki fazilat jaan letey to phir qura andazi key siwa koi chaara-kaar na paatey aur zarur (un do chizon key liye) qura andazi kartey. aur agar log jaan letey ke Zohar ki namaz jaldi padhney mein kya fazilat hai to eik doosrey sey aagey badhtey. aur agar utma ( Isha ) aur subh ki namaz ki fazilat jantey to zarur hazir hotey, chahey ghisat kar aana padta."
542,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Eirab (badwi log) tumhari is namaz ( Isha ) key naam key silsiley main tum par ghalib na aa jaeyn wo oonton ki wajeh sey us namaz ko muakhkhar kartey hain. bilashuba us namaz ka naam Isha hai."
543,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko member par ye farmatey huye suna : ye Erabi (dehati) (badwi log) tumhari us namaz key naam ( key mamley ) main tum par ghalib na aa jaeyn. khabrdar! bilashuba ye Isha hai.
544,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney subh ki namaz padhi jab subh aap key liye wazeh ho gaee.
545,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap sey subh ki namaz key waqt key barey mein puchha. jab agley din subh hui to junhi po phati, aap ney hukm diya ke namaz ki iqaamat kahi jaey aur hamen namaz padhaai. jab aglaa din huwa to aap ney roshni honey di. phir aap ney hukm diya to namaz ki iqaamat kahi gaee aur aap ney hamen namaz padhaai. phir aap ney farmaya : kahan hai wo shakhs jo namaz key waqt key barey mein sawal karta tha? un dono key darmiyan waqt hai."
546,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subh ki namaz sey farigh hotey to aurten apni chaadaron mein lipti hui gharon ko wapis jati thin aur andherey ki bina par pehchani na jati thin.
547,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke aurten Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath subh ki namaz apni chaadaron mein lipat kar padhti thin, phir wapis jatin to andherey ki bina par koi unhein pehchan nahin sakta tha."
548,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key din subh ki namaz andherey mein padhi jab ke aap khaibar key yahudiyon sey qarib they, phir aap ney un par hamla kya aur do dafa farmaya : « Allahu-akbar ! » khaibar wiran huwa. ( phir farmaya : ) bilashuba jab hum kisi qom key sehan ( maidan ) main utar padtey hain to un daraaey gaey logon ki subh bahut buri ho jati hai."
549,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : subh ( ki namaz ) ko roshan karo."
550,"Hazrat Mehmood bin Labid (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni qom ansaar key kaee buzurgon sey bayan kya ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Fajr ki namaz padhtey padhtey tum jis qadr bhi roshni karogey, wo tumharey liye sawab mein izaafey ka zaria hai."
551,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney subh ki namaz sey eik rakat suraj tulu honey sey qabl paa li to usney namaz paa li aur jis shakhs ney Asr ki namaz sey eik rakat suraj ghurub honey sey qabl paa li to usney namaz paa li."
552,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Fajr ki eik rakat tulu aaftaab sey qabl paa li to usney namaz paa li aur jis shakhs ney Asr ki eik rakat ghurub aaftaab sey qabl paa li to usney namaz paa li."
553,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki namaz padhtey they jab suraj dhalta tha. aur aap Asr ki namaz tumhari un do ( zuhar aur Asr ki ) namazon key darmiyan mein padhtey they. aur maghrib ki namaz padhtey jab suraj ghurub hota aur Isha ki namaz padhtey jab surkhi ghaayeb ho jati. phir unhoney uskey baad farmaya ke aap subh ki namaz sey us waqt farigh hotey jab nazar door tak dekhney lagti."
554,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney namaz ki eik rakat paa li, us ney namaz paa li."
555,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney namaz ki eik rakat paa li, us ney namaz paa li."
556,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney namaz ki eik rakat paa li, us ney namaz paa li."
557,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney namaz ki eik rakat paa li, us ney namaz paa li."
558,Hazrat Salim apney baap (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma) sey bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Juma ya kisi aur namaz ki eik rakat paa li to uski namaz puri ho gaee.
559,"Hazrat Salim sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kisi bhi namaz ki eik rakat paa li, us ney namaz paa li magar jitni namaz us sey reh gaee hai, usey puri kerega."
560,"Hazrat Abdullah sanaabihii (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj tulu hota hai to uskey sath shetan ka seeng bhi hota hai. phir jab suraj buland ho jata hai to shetan us sey door ho jata hai. phir jab suraj sar par aa jata hai to shetan uskey sath mil jata hai aur jab suraj dhal jata hai to shetan us sey alag ho jata hai. phir jab suraj ghurub honey key qarib hota hai to shetan phir us sey aa milta hai aur jab ghurub ho jata hai to shetan us sey door ho jata hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un oqaat mein namaz padhney sey roka hai."
561,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo farmatey hain : teen oqaat aisey hain jin mein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen namaz padhney ya maiyat key dafnaney sey mana kya hai : jab suraj roshan ho kar tulu ho raha ho yahan tak ke buland ho jaey aur jab suraj sar par khada ho yahan tak ke dhal jaey aur jab suraj ghurub honey key qarib ho yahan tak ke ghurub ho jaey."
562,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr ( ki namaz ) key baad namaz padhney sey roka hai yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey aur subh ( ki namaz ) key baad bhi namaz sey roka hai yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho jaey.
563,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya ke mainey bahut sey as-haabunnabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, un mein Hazrat umr bhi shamil hain aur wo mujhey un sab mein sab sey ziyada mehbub hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Fajr ki namaz key baad namaz padhney sey roka hai yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho jaey aur Asr ki namaz key baad bhi namaz padhney sey roka hai yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey."
564,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs qasdan tulu o ghurub shams key waqt namaz na padhey.
565,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya hai ke tulu o ghurub shams key waqt namaz padhi jaey.
566,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo farmatey hain : teen oqaat aisey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un mein hamen namaz padhney aur maiyat key dafn karney sey roka hai : jab suraj roshan ho kar tulu ho raha ho yahan tak ke buland ho jaey aur jab dophare key waqt suraj sar par khada ho yahan tak ke dhal jaey aur jab wo ghurub key waqt key qarib ho yahan tak ke ghurub ho jaey."
567,"Hazrat abu-Saeed khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney subh ki namaz key baad namaz padhney sey mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho jaey aur Asr key baad ghurub shams tak namaz sey mana farmaya hai."
568,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo farmatey hain : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Fajr ki namaz key baad koi namaz nahin yahan tak ke suraj saaf tulu ho jaey aur na Asr key baad namaz hai yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey."
569,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey usi qism ki riwayat bayan kartey hain.
570,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr key baad namaz padhney sey mana farmaya hai.
571,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghalat fehmi ho gaee (jo wo logon ko Asr key baad namaz padhney sey roktey hain) jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney to ye farmaya tha : tum qasdan tulu shams aur ghurub shams key waqt namaz na padho kyonkey suraj shetan key do seengon key darmiyan tulu hota hai.
572,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab suraj ki tikiya tulu honey lagey to namaz muakhkhar kar do yahan tak ke khub roshan ho jaey aur jab suraj ki tikiya ghurub honey lagey to namaz muakhkhar kar do yahan tak ke ghurub ho jaey.
573,"Hazrat abu-Umama Bahili (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kya koi ghhadi dusri ghhadi sey ziyada qurb wali hai? ya koi aisi ghhadi hai jis mein khususan Allah Taala ka zikr kya jaey ? aap ney farmaya : han, tehqiq Allah Taala apney bandey key sab sey ziyada qarib nisf raat key baad hota hai. agar tum taqat rakho ke us waqt Allah Taala ka zikr karney walon mein shamil ho to zarur aisa karo kyonkey us namaz mein farishtey hazir aur mojud hotey hain. ye waqt tulu shams tak rehta hai kyonkey suraj shetan key do seengon key darmiyan tulu hota hai aur ye kafiron ki ibadat ka waqt hai, lihaza us waqt namaz chhod do yahan tak ke suraj eik neze key b-qadr ooncha ho jaey aur uski shuaein khatm ho jaeyn. phir namaz ka waqt aa jata hai aur farishtey hazir hotey hain yahan tak ke suraj do-pahar key waqt neze ki tarah sidha sar par aa jata hai to us waqt jahannam key darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur jahannam ki aag bhadkai jati hai, chunanche tum namaz chhod do yahan tak ke saya dhal jaey, phir namaz ka waqt aa jata hai aur farishtey hazir hotey hain yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey kyonkey suraj shetan key do seengon key darmiyan ghurub hota hai aur ye kafiron ki namaz ka waqt hai."
574,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr key baad namaz padhney sey mana farmaya hai magar ye ke suraj safed, saaf aur buland ho."
575,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney merey yahan Asr key baad do rakatein kabhi nahin chodin۔
576,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi Asr ki namaz key baad merey yahan tashrif latey to ye do rakatein zarur padhtey
577,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi Asr ki namaz key baad merey paas hotey to ye do rakatein zarur padhtey
578,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke do namazein Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney merey ghar mein kabhi nahin choden, khufiya na elania. Fajr sey qabl do rakatein aur Asr key baad do rakatein."
579,Hazrat abu-Salma sey riwayat hai ke unhon ( abu-Salma ) ney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey un do rakaat key barey mein puchha jo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Asr key baad padha kartey they. to unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye do rakatein Asr sey pehley padha kartey they. phir eik din kisi masrufiyat mein aap sey ye do rakat reh gaeen ya aap bhool gaey to aap ney Asr key baad unhein padha. aur aap jab koi namaz eik dafa padh letey to is par pabandi farmatey they.
580,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey ghar mein sirf eik dafa Asr key baad do rakatein padhin unhoney aap sey us ka zikr kya to aap ney farmaya : ye wo rakatein hain jo main Zohar key baad padha karta hun. aaj main un sey masruf raha yahan tak ke Asr ka waqt ho gaya aur mujhey Asr padhni padi.
581,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (eik din) Asr sey pehley (Zohar key baad) ki do rakaton sey masroof rahey to aap ney unhein Asr key baad ada farmaya.
582,"Hazrat Imran bin hudair ney Hazrat laahiq sey ghurub shams sey qabl ki do rakaaton key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma ye do rakatein padha kartey they to Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein pegham bheja ke ghurub aaftab key waqt ye do rakatein kaisi hain? baat Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) tak pahunchi to unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye do rakatein Asr sey pehley padha kartey they. (eik din ) aap masroofiyat ki bina par na padh sakey to aap ney ghurub shams key waqt ( Asr key baad ) ye do rakatein padh lein. mainey us din key siwa kabhi aap ko ye do rakatein padhtey nahin dekha. us sey pehley, na baad."
583,Abul-Khair sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Tamim Jishani maghrib ( ki namaz ) sey pehley do rakatein padhney key liye uthey . mainey Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : unhein dekhiye ye kon si namaz padh rahey hain? unhon ( Aqba ) ney un ki taraf tawajjoh farmaai to unhein ( namaz padhtey ) dekha to unhoney farmaya ke hum ye namaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamana mubarak mein padha kartey they.
584,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab Fajr tulu ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sirf do halki rakatein padhtey they.
585,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ( sab sey pehley) aap par kon eman laya ? aap ney farmaya : eik azad ( abu-Bakar Siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ) aur eik ghulam (Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ). mainey kaha : kya koi waqt Allah Taala key yahan doosrey waqt sey ziyada qurb wala hai? aap ney farmaya : han, raat ka aakhiri nisf lihaza tum namaz padho jis qadr tum chaho yahan tak ke tum subh ki namaz padho, phir suraj tulu honey tak ruk jao jab tak ke wo dhaal ki tarah rahey. jab wo phel jaey to jis qadr chaho namaz padho yahan tak ke sutun apney saye par khada ho jaey. phir ruk jao yahan tak ke suraj dhal jaey kyonkey do-pahar key waqt jahannam bhadkaya jata hai, phir jis qadr chaho namaz padho yahan tak ke Asr ki namaz padh lo, phir ruk jao yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey kyonkey wo shetan key do seengon key darmiyan tulu o ghurub hota hai."
586,"Hazrat Juber bin mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey bani Abd-Manaaf ! tum kisi ko na roko jo us ghar ka tawaf karey aur namaz padhey, din ya raat key jis waqt mein chahey."
587,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab suraj dhalney sey pehley safar shuru kartey to Zohar ki namaz ko Asr key waqt tak muakhkhar kartey, phir utartey aur dono ko ikhatta kartey aur agar safar shuru karney sey qabl suraj dhal jata to Zohar ki namaz padh kar sawari farmatey."
588,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke hum ghazwa tabuk key saal (9 hijri mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath nikley to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar aur Asr ko aur maghrib aur Isha ko jama farmaya kartey they. eik din aap ney Zohar ki namaz ko muakhkhar farmaya, phir bahar tashrif laye aur Zohar aur Asr ikhatti padhein phir andar chaley gaey, phir tashrif laye aur maghrib aur Isha ikhatti kar key padhin"
589,"Janab Kasir bin Qarwanda sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah sey unkey walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma) ki doraney-safar ki namaz key barey mein puchha ke kya wo safar key doran mein namazon ko jama kartey they? to unhoney bataya ke Hazrat Safiya bint abi Ubaid merey walid mohtaram key nikah mein thin. unhoney walid mohtaram ko likha, jab ke aap apni zamin mein they, ke main duniya key dino mein sey aakhiri aur aakhirat key dino mein sey pehley din mein hun. ( yani qaribul-marg hun, aap tashrif laaiye) chunanche aap fauran sawar huye aur badi tezi sey un ki taraf chaley yahan tak ke jab namaz Zohar ka waqt huwa to un sey muazzan ney kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehmaan! namaz padh lijiye. lekin aap ney tawajjoh na farmaai yahan tak ke jab do namazon (Zohar aur Asr) ka darmiyan huwa to utrey aur farmaya : iqaamat kaho aur jab main (Zohar ki) namaz sey salam pher lun to phir (Asr ki) iqaamat keh dena. is tarah namazein padhin phir dobara sawar huye yahan tak ke jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to muazzan ney aap sey kaha ke namaz padh lijiye. aap ney farmaya : jis tarah Zohar aur Asr mein kya tha, isi tarah ab karna yahan tak ke jab tarey gehrey aur ghaney ho gaey to utrey, phir muazzan sey kaha : iqaamat kaho. phir jab main (maghrib ki namaz sey) salam pher lun to (Isha key liye) iqaamat keh dena. isi tarah dono namazein padhin phir farigh huye to hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jab tum mein sey kisi ko koi aisa kaam pad jaey jis key zaya honey ka khatra ho to wo is tarah namazein padhey."
590,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madina Munawra mein aath rakatein ikhatti aur saat rakatein ikhatti padhin aap ney Zohar ko muakhkhar kya aur Asr ko jaldi padha, isi tarah maghrib ko muakhkhar kya aur Isha ko jaldi padha."
591,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke unhoney Basra mein Zohar aur Asr ko is tarah padha ke unkey darmiyan koi fasla nahin tha aur maghrib aur Isha ko bhi isi tarah padha ke unkey darmiyan koi fasla nahin tha. aap ney ye kaam kisi masroofiyat ki bina par kya tha, neez unhoney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madina Munawra mein Zohar aur Asr ki aath rakaat padhin aur unkey darmiyan koi fasla nahin tha."
592,"Quraish key eik buzurg Ismail bin Abdur-Rehman ney kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key sath «Hima» ( Madina Munawra sey qarib eik charagah ) tak raha. jab suraj ghurub ho gaya to main darta hi raha ke aap sey kahun ke namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai. aap chaltey rahey yahan tak ke maghribi kinarey ki safedi khatam ho gaee aur Isha (raat ) ki siyahi aa gaee. phir aap utrey aur maghrib ki namaz teen rakaat padhin. phir uskey baad Isha ki do rakaat padhin, phir farmaya ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey kartey huye dekha hai."
593,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap ko safar mein chalney ki jaldi hoti to maghrib ki namaz ko muakhkhar kartey yahan tak ke usey aur Isha ki namaz ko ikhatta padhtey
594,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke suraj ghurub huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama mein they magar aap ney dono namazein ( maqaam ) Sarf mein jama kin.
595,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko jab chalney ki jaldi hoti to aap Zohar ki namaz ko Asr key waqt tak muakhkhar kartey, phir dono ko ikhatta padhtey isi tarah maghrib ki namaz ko muakhkhar kartey yahan tak ke jab surkhi ghayab ho jati usey aur Isha ki namaz ko ikhatta padhtey"
596,"Hazrat Naafey (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key sath eik safar mein nikla. aap apni zamin mein jana chahtey they. itney main eik aaney wala aaya aur us ney kaha : tehqiq Safiya binte Abu-Ubaid (ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki biwi) bahut tang (takleef mein) hain, jaldi chalen taake aap unhein (zindagi mein) mil saken. ibne-Umar jaldi chaley aur unkey sath Quraish key eik aur buzurg bhi safar kar rahey they. suraj ghurub ho gaya magar unhon (ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma) ney namaz na padhi jab ke mainey aap ko hamesha dekha tha ke aap namaz ki bahut pabandi kartey they. jab aap ney ziyada der ki to mainey kaha : namaz padh lijiye Allah Taala aap par reham farmaai ! aap ney meri taraf dekha aur chaltey rahey yahan tak ke jab surkhi ghaaieb honey ko hui to aap utrey aur maghrib ki namaz padhi, phir Isha ki iqaamat kahlwaai jab ke surkhi ghaaieb ho chuki thi aur hamein Isha ki namaz padhaai phir hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko jab chalney ki jaldi hoti to aap aisey kiya kartey they."
597,"Hazrat Naafey (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key sath Makka Mukarrama sey aaye. us raat aap chaltey rahey yahan tak ke Sham ho gaee. hamney samjha ke aap namaz bhool gaey hain. hamney aap sey kaha : namaz padhiye ! aap chup rahey aur chaltey rahey yahan tak ke qarib tha ke surkhi ghaaieb ho jati phir aap utrey aur maghrib ki namaz padhi, itney mein surkhi bhi ghaaieb ho gaee, phir aap ney Isha ki namaz padhi. phir hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath aisey hi kiya kartey they jab aap ko chalney ki jaldi hoti thi."
598,"Hazrat Kasir bin Qarwanda ney kaha ke hamney Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah sey safar ki namaz key barey mein puchha hamney kaha : kya Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma safar mein namazon ko jama kartey they? unhoney kaha : nahin siwaye muzdalfa key. phir wo chaunkey aur kehney lagey : unkey nikah mein Safiya binte Abu-Ubaid thin. unhoney aap ko pegham bheja ke main duniya key aakhiri din aur aakhirat key pehley din mein hun, chunanche aap sawar huye. main bhi aap key sath tha. wo bahut tezi sey chaley yahan tak ke namaz ka waqt aa gaya. muazzan ney aap sey kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! namaz padh lijiye. aap chaltey rahey yahan tak ke jab do namazon ka darmiyani waqt aa gaya to aap utrey aur muazzan sey kaha ke iqaamat kaho. jab main Zohar ki namaz sey salam phairun to usi jagah iqaamat keh dena. us ney iqaamat kahi to aap ney Zohar ki namaz do rakat padhein, phir salam pheraa , phir usi jagah Asr ki iqaamat kahlwaai aur Asr ki namaz do rakat padhein, phir sawar ho gaey aur khub tez chaley yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya. muazzan ney kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! namaz padhiye. aap ney farmaya : jis tarah tu ney pehley kiya hai isi tarah karna. phir aap chaltey rahey yahan tak ke sitarey ghaney ho gaey to utrey aur farmaya ke iqaamat keh, phir jab main (Namaze Maghrib sey) salam pherun to phir takbir kehna. us ney iqaamat kahi to aap ney Maghrib ki teen rakatein padhein, phir us ney usi jagah iqaamat kahi to aap ney Isha ki namaz padhi, phir aap ney samney ki taraf eik dafa salam kaha, phir kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko aisa kaam pad jaey jis key zaya honey ka usey khatra ho to wo is tarah namaz padhey."
599,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko safar par janey ki jaldi hoti to Maghrib aur Isha ko jama farmatey.
600,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko chalney ki jaldi hoti ya koi masla aap ko be-chain karta to aap Maghrib aur Isha ko jama farmatey.
601,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke mainey dekha, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko chalney ki jaldi hoti to aap Maghrib aur Isha ko jama farmatey."
602,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney baghair kisi khof aur safar key Zohar aur Asr ki namazein ikhatti padhein, isi tarah maghrib aur Isha ki namazein bhi ikhatti padhein."
603,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Madina Munawra mein Zohar aur Asr aur maghrib aur Isha baghair kisi khof aur barish key ikhatti kar key padhein kaha gaya : kyon? unhoney farmaya : taake aap ki ummat par tangi na ho.
604,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey aath aur saat rakatein ikhatti padhi hain.
605,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) chaltey rahey yahan tak ke arfa pahunch gaey. aap ney apna khema wadi namra mein laga huwa paya. aap is mein utrey yahan tak ke jab suraj dhal gaya to aap ney hukm diya, aap ki oontni qaswaa par paalaan kasaa gaya yahan tak ke jab aap wadi key pet mein pahunch gaey to logon ko khutba diya, phir Bilal ney Azan kahi phir iqaamat kahi. aap ney Zohar ki namaz padhaai phir unhoney iqaamat kahi to aap ney Asr ki namaz padhaai aur in dono key darmiyan kuchh nahin padha."
606,Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : mainey Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par muzdalfa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Maghrib aur Isha ki namazein mila kar padhein.
607,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber farmatey hain ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key sath tha jab wo arafat sey wapis lotey aur jab wo muzdalfa aaye to unhoney Maghrib aur Isha ko jama kiya. jab farigh huye to farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is maqam par aisey hi kiya tha, yani ye do namazein ikhatti padhi thin."
608,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muzdalfa mein maghrib aur Isha ikhatti padhein.
609,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi do namazein jama kar key padhtey nahin dekha magar muzdalfa mein. aap ney us din subah ki namaz (apney mamool key) waqt sey pehley padhi.
610,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Arafat sey wapsi par unhein apney peechhey oont par bithaya huwa tha, ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Arafat aur muzdalfa key darmiyan aaney wali) ghaati par pahunchey to aap utrey aur peshab kiya. phir mainey lotey sey pani dala aur aap ney halka sa wuzu farmaya. mainey aap sey guzarish ki ke namaz padh lijiye. aap ney farmaya : namaz aagey hogi. jab Muzdalfa tashrif laye to Maghrib ki namaz padhaai phir sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney sawaariyon sey paalaan waghera utarey phir aap ney Isha ki namaz padhaai."
611,Hazrat Abu-Amr Shebaani ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar ki taraf ishara kar key farmaya : hamen is ghar key Malik ney bayan farmaya ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kon sa amal Allah Taala ko ziyada pasand hai? aap ney farmaya : waqt par namaz padhna waliden sey husne-sulook karna aur Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karna.
612,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kon sa amal Allah Taala ko ziyada pasand hai? aap ney farmaya : waqt par namaz qaaim karna  waliden sey husne-sulook karna aur Allah key raastey mein jihad karna.
613,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muntashir bayan kartey hain ke wo Hazrat Amr bin Shurehbil ki masjid mein they ke jamaat key liye iqaamat kahi gaee. phir log unka intizar karney lagey. (woh aaye to) unhoney farmaya : main witr padh raha tha. unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya : kya Azaan-Fajr key baad witr padh saktey hain? unhoney farmaya : han, balke iqaamat key baad bhi phir unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka waqiyaa bayan farmaya ke eik din aap namaz Fajr sey soey rahey yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho gaya, phir aap ney namaz ada farmaee. ye lafz Yahya key hain."
614,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi koi namaz bhool jaey to jab yad aaye padh ley.
615,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us aadmi key barey mein puchha gaya jo namaz sey soyaa rehta hai ya ghafil ho jata hai (bhool jata hai). aap ney farmaya is ka kaffara ye hai ke jab usey yad aaye, namaz padh ley."
616,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke sahaba ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr kiya ke kabhi hum namaz sey soey rehtey hain. aap ney farmaya : neend aa janey mein qusur aur kotahi nahin. kotahi to ye hai ke aadmi jaagta huwa namaz na padhey chunanche jab tum mein sey koi namaz bhool jaey ya us sey soyaa reh jaey to jab usey yad aaye (ya jaagey) to usi waqt namaz padh ley.
617,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : neend aa janey mein kotahi nahin. kotahi to us shakhs mein hai jisney agli namaz ka waqt aaney tak namaz na padhi, halanke wo jaag raha tha."
618,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab sahaba subah ki namaz sey soey reh gaey they yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho gaya tha to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha ke kal tum ye namaz iskey waqt par padhna.
619,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum namaz bhool jao to jab yad aaye padh lo kyonkey Allah Taala (Quran Majeed mein) farmata hai : (واقم الصلوۃ لذکری),''aur meri yad aaney par namaz qaaim karo.'' Abdul-A'alaa ney kaha : hamein ye riwayat Hazrat Yala ney ikhtisaar key sath bayan ki."
620,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs namaz bhool jaey to usey chahiye ke usey yad aaney par padh ley kyonkey Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : ( واقم الصلوۃ لذکری ), ''aur meri yad aaney par namaz padho.''"
621,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs namaz bhool jaey to usey jab yad aaye, usi waqt padh ley kyonkey Allah Taala farmata hai : ( اقم الصلاۃ لذکری ),''yaad aaney par namaz qaaim karo.'' Ma'mar kehtey hain ke mainey Imam Zohri sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney isi tarah qirat farmaai thi? unhoney kaha : haan."
622,"Hazrat Abu Mariyam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. hum sari raat chaltey rahey. jab subah tulu honey ko thi to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sawari sey utrey aur so gaey aur log bhi so gaey. hamein us waqt jaag aai jab suraj hum par tulu ho chuka tha, chunanche Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muazzan ko hukm diya to usney Azan kahi, phir aap ney Fajr ki do sunnatein padhein, phir aap ney usey hukm diya to usney iqaamat kahi, phir aap ney logon ko namaz padhaai phir hamein bayan kiya jo kuchh qiyamat tak honey wala tha."
623,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. hum Zohar, Asr, Maghrib aur Isha ki namaz na padh sakey. ye baat merey liye bahut takleef deh thi. mainey apney dil mein kaha ke hum Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath aur Allah Taala key raastey mein hain. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya. unhoney iqaamat kahi to aap ney hamen Zohar ki namaz padhaai, phir iqaamat kahi to aap ney hamen Asr ki namaz padhaai, phir iqaamat kahi to aap ney hamen maghrib ki namaz padhaai, phir iqaamat kahi to aap ney hamen Isha ki namaz padhaai, phir hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : ruey zamin par tumharey ilawa koi jamaat (is waqt ) Allah Taala ka zikr nahin kar rahi hai."
624,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (eik din doraney-safar mein) hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath aakhir raat mein padaaw dala aur hum na jaagey yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho gaya. (jaagney par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har aadmi apni sawari ka sar pakdey (yahan sey kooch kerey) kyonkey is maqam mein shetan hamarey paas raha hai. hamney isi tarah kiya (wahan sey nikal gaey).  phir aap ney pani mangwayaa aur wuzu kiya, phir do rakatein (sunnate Fajr) padhein phir jamaat ki iqaamat kahi gaee aur aap ney subah ki namaz padhaai."
625,Hazrat Juber (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik safar mein ( aakhir raat mein sotey waqt ) farmaya : is raat kon hamarey liye Fajr ki namaz ka khayal rakheyga? kahin hum namaz sey soey hi na reh jaeyn. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main. phir wo tulu shams ke nikalne ki taraf munh kar key beth gaey. Allah Taala ney sab ko sulaa diya yahan tak ke unhein suraj ki garmi ney jagaya. tab wo uthey. aap ney farmaya : wuzu karo. phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney Azan kahi. aap ney do rakatein padhein aur dusrey logon ney bhi Fajr ki sunnatein padhein phir sab ney Fajr ki namaz (baa-jamaa't ) padhi.
626,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) shuru raat mein chaley phir aakhir raat aap ney padaaw dala. aap bar-waqt jaag na sakey yahan tak ke kuchh ya sara suraj tulu ho gaya, chunanche aap ney fauran namaz na padhi yahan tak ke suraj buland ho gaya to aap ney namaz ada farmaai aur ye (Namaze Fajr) salaatul-wustaa hai."
